summary:
I started repairing and maintaining personal computers and operative systems, like windows, after this I grew up on the path of web aplications, using Debian servers connecting via ssh, and linux as my main operative system, with programming tools like php, javascript, mysql, html. Also experience with Visual Basic and C# in windows with Visual Studio. (.NET). 
You can see some of my works: https://github.com/gutic
I just arrived in the Netherlands. I have two nationalities: Dutch and Argentine. At this moment I'm open for new  job opportunities in the Netherlands in the role of developer. My native language is Spanish and on a daily basis I speak fluent English. Already busy with learning the Dutch language.
